    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term referring to several species of carnivorous dinosaurs that walk on two legs, including Velociraptor, Deinonychus, Oviraptor, Dromaeosaurus, Gigantoraptor, among others.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
